<div class="container-fluid giant-container pb-5">

    <div class="display-header-layout container-fluid mb-5">
        <div class="container-sm heading-container">
            <div class="heading-line"></div>
            <h1 class="heading-with-lines display-1">Sustainability</h1>
            <div class="heading-line"></div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="small-card-layout container-fluid">
        <div class="container-sm">
            <div class="row perspective-container">
                <div class="col-lg-3 col-md-6 mb-4">
                    <div class="card text-center perspective-card-small hidden" id="card1">
                        <div class="card-body">
                            <div class="card-icon">🧑‍🌾</div>
                            <h5 class="card-title">Vedic Farming For Soil Health</h5>
                            <p class="card-text">Emphasizing natural methods to maintain soil fertility without chemicals.</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="col-lg-3 col-md-6 mb-4">
                    <div class="card text-center perspective-card-small hidden" id="card2">
                        <div class="card-body">
                            <div class="card-icon">🌱</div>
                            <h5 class="card-title">Companion Planting For Pest Control</h5>
                            <p class="card-text">Using nature to protect crops, like planting turmeric with ginger to ward off pests.</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="col-lg-3 col-md-6 mb-4">
                    <div class="card text-center perspective-card-small hidden" id="card3">
                        <div class="card-body">
                            <div class="card-icon">💧</div>
                            <h5 class="card-title">Sustainable Water Management</h5>
                            <p class="card-text">Utilizing ancient stepwells to efficiently store and manage water.</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="col-lg-3 col-md-6 mb-4">
                    <div class="card text-center perspective-card-small hidden" id="card4">
                        <div class="card-body">
                            <div class="card-icon">🌳</div>
                            <h5 class="card-title">Agroforestry For Biodiversity</h5>
                            <p class="card-text">Integrating trees and crops to foster a healthy, biodiverse environment.</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    

    <div class="wide-carousel-layout container-fluid mb-5">
        <div class="container-sm">
            <div id="wide-carousel" class="carousel slide carousel-fade" data-bs-ride="carousel">
                <div class="carousel-indicators">
                    <button type="button" data-bs-target="#wide-carousel" data-bs-slide-to="0" class="active" aria-current="true" aria-label="Slide 1"></button>
                    <button type="button" data-bs-target="#wide-carousel" data-bs-slide-to="1" aria-label="Slide 2"></button>
                </div>
                <div class="carousel-inner">
                    <div class="carousel-item active">
                        <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1572587356426-b33bf42f999b?q=80&w=1771&auto=format&fit=crop&ixlib=rb-4.0.3&ixid=M3wxMjA3fDB8MHxwaG90by1wYWdlfHx8fGVufDB8fHx8fA%3D%3D" alt="Slide 1">
                        <div class="carousel-caption mb-2">
                            <h5>Farm-To-Table Sourcing with Ancient Indian Techniques</h5>
                            <p>
                                The restaurant sources fresh, organic produce grown on a Texas farm using ancient Indian farming techniques like Vedic farming. This method emphasizes soil health, natural growth, and chemical-free practices.
                            </p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="carousel-item">
                        <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1482685945432-29a7abf2f466?q=80&w=1789&auto=format&fit=crop&ixlib=rb-4.0.3&ixid=M3wxMjA3fDB8MHxwaG90by1wYWdlfHx8fGVufDB8fHx8fA%3D%3D" alt="Slide 2">
                        <div class="carousel-caption mb-2">
                            <h5>Traditional Water Conservation Methods (like Stepwells and Wells)</h5>
                            <p>
                                Ancient Indian farming traditions focused heavily on water conservation, especially in dry, arid regions. The farm utilizes techniques inspired by the stepwell system used in ancient India to store and distribute water. These systems allow the farm to efficiently collect and store rainwater, reducing reliance on external water sources and ensuring that crops thrive with little water waste.
                            </p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <button class="carousel-control-prev" type="button" data-bs-target="#wide-carousel" data-bs-slide="prev">
                    <span class="carousel-control-prev-icon" aria-hidden="true"></span>
                    <span class="visually-hidden">Previous</span>
                </button>
                <button class="carousel-control-next" type="button" data-bs-target="#wide-carousel" data-bs-slide="next">
                    <span class="carousel-control-next-icon" aria-hidden="true"></span>
                    <span class="visually-hidden">Next</span>
                </button>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    


    <div class="big-number-layout container-fluid mb-5">
        <div class="container-sm position-relative text-center">
            <div class="giant-percentage">90%</div>
            <div class="small-text fs-3">90% of the produce we use that comes from our own farms.</div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="quote-layout container-fluid mb-5">
        <div class="container-sm">
            <figure class="text-center pt-2 border-top border-bottom">
                <blockquote class="blockquote">
                    <p>By combining ancient wisdom with modern methods, we’re building a sustainable future, one crop at a time.</p>
                </blockquote>
                <figcaption class="blockquote-footer">
                    The White Tiger Team
                </figcaption>
            </figure>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="carousel-with-text-layout container-fluid mb-5">
        <div class="container-sm">
            <div class="row">
                <div class="col-md-12 col-lg-6">
                    <div id="carousel-with-text" class="carousel slide carousel-fade" data-bs-ride="carousel">
                        <div class="carousel-indicators">
                            <button type="button" data-bs-target="#carousel-with-text" data-bs-slide-to="0" class="active" aria-current="true" aria-label="Slide 1"></button>
                            <button type="button" data-bs-target="#carousel-with-text" data-bs-slide-to="1" aria-label="Slide 2"></button>
                            <button type="button" data-bs-target="#carousel-with-text" data-bs-slide-to="2" aria-label="Slide 3"></button>
                        </div>
                        <div class="carousel-inner">
                            <div class="carousel-item active">
                                <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1603329470128-074eaf2939e7?q=80&w=1770&auto=format&fit=crop&ixlib=rb-4.0.3&ixid=M3wxMjA3fDB8MHxwaG90by1wYWdlfHx8fGVufDB8fHx8fA%3D%3D" alt="Slide 1">
                            </div>
                            <div class="carousel-item">
                                <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1655409703097-78a27bed8b38?q=80&w=1770&auto=format&fit=crop&ixlib=rb-4.0.3&ixid=M3wxMjA3fDB8MHxwaG90by1wYWdlfHx8fGVufDB8fHx8fA%3D%3D" alt="Slide 2">
                            </div>
                            <div class="carousel-item">
                                <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1657667779190-8e90af2d9f3f?q=80&w=1932&auto=format&fit=crop&ixlib=rb-4.0.3&ixid=M3wxMjA3fDB8MHxwaG90by1wYWdlfHx8fGVufDB8fHx8fA%3D%3D" alt="Slide 3">
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <button class="carousel-control-prev" type="button" data-bs-target="#carousel-with-text" data-bs-slide="prev">
                            <span class="carousel-control-prev-icon" aria-hidden="true"></span>
                            <span class="visually-hidden">Previous</span>
                        </button>
                        <button class="carousel-control-next" type="button" data-bs-target="#carousel-with-text" data-bs-slide="next">
                            <span class="carousel-control-next-icon" aria-hidden="true"></span>
                            <span class="visually-hidden">Next</span>
                        </button>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="col-md-12 col-lg-6">
                    <h2>
                        Sustainably Harvesting Water From Sacred Wells
                    </h2>
                    <div class="little-line"></div>
                    <p>
                        In ancient Indian villages, wells and tanks were used for sustainable water management. Our farm uses similar traditional well techniques to store rainwater and allow it to seep into the earth naturally, reducing evaporation and ensuring crops are properly watered during dry periods.
                    </p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="quote-layout container-fluid mb-5">
        <div class="container-sm">
            <div class="d-flex quote-layout-container" style="gap: 20px;">
                <div class="line"></div>
                <div class="quote-text-div">
                    <h3>
                        In Summary
                    </h3>
                    <p>
                        <strong>Farm-To-Table Sourcing with Ancient Indian Techniques:</strong> Our produce is grown using Vedic farming, promoting soil health and natural growth, free from synthetic chemicals.
                    </p>
                    <p>
                        <strong>Traditional Water Conservation Techniques:</strong> Inspired by ancient stepwells, we store and manage water to minimize waste and ensure crops thrive even in dry climates.
                    </p>
                    <p>
                        <strong>Agroforestry:</strong> We use agroforestry to plant multiple crops alongside trees, maximizing land productivity and preserving biodiversity.
                    </p>
                    <p>
                        <strong>Sustainably Harvestng Water From Sacred Wells:</strong> The farm uses traditional water harvesting techniques to maintain water efficiency in a region often subject to drought.
                    </p>
                    <p>
                        <strong>Using Cow Dung In Soil Fertility:</strong> We enrich the soil naturally using organic cow dung, promoting microbial activity without the need for harmful chemicals.
                    </p>
                    <p>
                        <strong>Companion Planting For Natural Fertility & Pest Control:</strong> Using traditional companion planting methods, crops naturally support one another to improve soil health and protect against pests.
                    </p>
                    <p>
                        <strong>Promoting Biodiversity Through Desi Seeds:</strong> We conserve indigenous and drought-resistant seeds that thrive in the Texas climate, ensuring sustainable farming practices.
                    </p>
                    <p>
                        <strong>Sustainable harvestng Of Water From Sacred Wells:</strong> The farm uses traditional water harvesting techniques to maintain water efficiency in a region often subject to drought.
                    </p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>


</div>

